{
  "page": "Long Canal",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Long Canal</b> is a large canal in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>. Beginning in the south of the city's lagoon near the fishmarket, it extends north under the <a href=\"/index.php/Sweetwater_river\" title=\"Sweetwater river\">sweetwater river</a> and several bridges with the <a href=\"/index.php/Silty_Town\" title=\"Silty Town\">Silty Town</a> to the east.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It then reaches the heart of the city, with the <a href=\"/index.php/Palace_of_Truth\" title=\"Palace of Truth\">Palace of Truth</a> to the northeast and the <a href=\"/index.php/Sept-Beyond-the-Sea\" title=\"Sept-Beyond-the-Sea\">Sept-Beyond-the-Sea</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Black_and_White\" title=\"House of Black and White\">House of Black and White</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_the_Gods\" title=\"Isle of the Gods\">Isle of the Gods</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_the_Lord_of_Light_(Braavos)\" title=\"Temple of the Lord of Light (Braavos)\">Temple of the Lord of Light</a> to the northwest. The <a href=\"/index.php/Canal_of_Heroes\" title=\"Canal of Heroes\">Canal of Heroes</a> flows into this city center from the west.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The towers of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Antaryon\" title=\"House Antaryon\">Antaryons</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Prestayn\" title=\"House Prestayn\">Prestayns</a> are located near the Long Canal.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Long_Canal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Long_Canal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> travels the Long Canal with <a href=\"/index.php/Yorko\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Yorko\">Yorko</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/index.php/Brusco\" title=\"Brusco\">Brusco</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Long_Canal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-c